OL,5,CColleges Wales
OL,7,F"That's a huge impact. It's about half
OL,8,Fthe programme overall and obviously
OL,9,Fthe impact is on the wider economy as
OL,10,Fwell.
OL,12,F"We think about #90 million will be
OL,13,Flost to the Welsh economy in the short
OL,14,Fterm and over the long term probably
OL,15,F#400 million lost to the Welsh economy
OL,16,Fas a result of these cuts this year."
