OL,3,C'10,000 fewer people to start
OL,4,Capprenticeships this year', says
OL,5,CColleges Wales
OL,7,FThe has spent years encouraging people
OL,8,Fto embark on apprenticeships and had
OL,9,Fset a target of 125,000 new starters
OL,10,Fin apprenticeships by the end of the
OL,11,Fcurrent Senedd term.
OL,13,FHowever that target has already been
OL,14,Frevised down and the draft Welsh
OL,15,FGovernment budget has now slashed
OL,16,Ffunding for apprenticeships.
OL,18,FMr Hagendyk said he understands the
OL,19,Ffinancial constraints facing the
OL,20,Fgovernment at this time but he called
OL,21,Fon politicians to reconsider the cuts.
