OL,3,C'10,000 fewer people to start
OL,4,Capprenticeships this year', says
OL,5,CColleges Wales
OL,7,FHe said: "It's driven by real cost
OL,8,Fpressures. It's driven by the loss of
OL,9,FEuropean social funding that was there
OL,10,Fin previous years.
OL,12,F"But we think it's short-sighted and
OL,13,Fit needs to be reversed in some way."
OL,15,FOn Monday the Senedd's Economy, Trade
OL,16,Fand Rural Affairs Committee released a
OL,17,Freport on the draft budget which
OL,18,Fraised concerns about the economic
OL,19,Fimpact of cuts to apprenticeships.
